        "created_at": "2022-09-03T02:46:16.520Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thanks for the note.  I agree with you - he is a very talented winemaker, and his profile is growing\u2026 I think <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/william_kelley\">@William_Kelley</a> just reviewed his range (for the first time if I am not mistaken).</p>\n<p>It is also worth trying the C+C from the same base year side by side with the Oiry - they have different profiles.</p>",
