        "created_at": "2022-09-03T15:22:39.566Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Will definitely check out C+C when given the chance.</p>\n<p>As this wine warmed a bit in the glass it did pick up some \u2018cheese\u2019, brioche, rich/opulent characteristics, so this particular Champagne I personally prefer cold versus cellar - much more interesting to me at the cooler temperature</p>",
